venue.address_1: 7 VFW Parkway (Parking lot at Our Lady of Annunciation Church)
venue.name: Allandale Urban Wild

item.description:
Join Boston Natural Areas Network for a magical fall naturalist-guided tour through one of Boston's most cherished urban wilds and then exercise your stewardship muscles by planting native trees and shrubs. We will provide gloves, tools and something warm to drink.

For more information call: 617-542-7696 or email karen@bostonnatural.org
item.name: Autumn Tour and Tree Planting at Allandale Urban Wild
